tion as low as 3.5 {\\AA}. Though no algorithm of\nstructure solution has been figured out based on the latter function, the\nresults presented here provide a new perspective on the phase problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Mar 2015 12:18:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 May 2015 07:52:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-14"}
