 barrier\nor the dust sublimation lines. These planet traps may temporarily favor the\ngrowth of planetary cores.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Mar 2015 14:33:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-06"}
